Marjoe (1972), Directed by Sarah Kernochan and Howard Smith

IMDB: http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0068924/

Part documentary, part expose, this film follows one-time child
evangelist Marjoe Gortner on the "church tent" Revivalist circuit,
commenting on the showmanship of Evangelism and "the religion
business", prior to the start of "televangelism".
